  "name": "Dendrology",
  "shortName": "dendrology",
  "description": "<i>Dendrology</i> is a variant of well known <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Minesweeper\">Minesweeper</a> game. The gameplay takes place on a 10x10 fields board. The main task requires planting the trees in a proper way by using principles of nature. The trees can't grow too close to each other as they will compete for resources. The start screen is filled with some digits. The digits shows how many neighbour fields (horizontally, vertically, diagonally) must contain trees. The trees can't touch each other, and there is only one proper global solution.",
